OL,3,CLiberal Democrats name candidate for
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats have announced
OL,7,Fthat councillor Richard Kilpatrick
OL,8,Fwill be their candidate in the Greater
OL,9,FManchester mayoral by-election
OL,10,Ftriggered by the election of Andy
OL,11,FBurnham as MP.
OL,13,FFormerly a teacher, Mr Kilpatrick
OL,14,Fserved as a councillor in Didsbury
OL,15,FWest for the past eight years.
OL,17,FHe said he is thrilled to have been
OL,18,Fselected: "Our region has so much
OL,19,Fpotential but voters have been let
OL,20,Fdown by Labour's complacency, whilst
OL,21,Fall Reform offer is division.
OL,26,@zD@KOU
