OL,3,CLiberal Democrats name candidate for
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,F"In this election we have a real
OL,7,Fopportunity to champion the issues
OL,8,Fthat matter most to people, from
OL,9,Fmaking transport more affordable,
OL,10,Finvesting in social care and restoring
OL,11,Fneighbourhood policing to truly make
OL,12,Fpeople in our community feel safe."
OL,14,FThe Liberal Democrats are campaigning
OL,15,Ffor an immediate package to help
OL,16,Fhouseholds across Greater Manchester
OL,17,Fwho are struggling with the cost of
OL,18,Fliving crisis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@cO]
