OL,3,CLiberal Democrats name candidate for
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FCllr Kilpatrick also wants to see more
OL,7,Finvestment in social care, more
OL,8,Faffordable public transport and
OL,9,Fimprovements to community policing.
OL,11,FThree other political parties have
OL,12,Fannounced their candidates for the
OL,13,Fmayoral race.
OL,15,FThe vote will take place on 30 July
OL,16,F2026.
OL,18,FThe successful candidate will hold
OL,19,Foffice until the next scheduled
OL,20,Felection for the mayoralty in May 2028.
